item.title: My Week in Music #6: 2018/11/09 - 2018/11/16
item.description: Last.fm is a website that can keep track of users and their listening habits. I’ve been listening to music with Last.fm since 2010 and am slightly obsessive over my music stats. These stats are for my listening from the past week. My week for November 09, 2018 to November 16, 2018 Top 10 Artists Top 10 Artists L’Arc~en~Ciel (+3) Coheed and Cambria is finally dethroned!
